WEBVTT

1
00:00:28.541 --> 00:00:29.375
Dad...

2
00:00:29.458 --> 00:00:30.708
Dad. let's go home.

3
00:00:30.791 --> 00:00:31.916
So I can explain...

4
00:00:36.458 --> 00:00:37.458
Just look at him.

5
00:00:49.875 --> 00:00:51.541
Thando. do you think this is a joke?

6
00:00:58.416 --> 00:00:59.875
- Let me help you...
- No!

7
00:01:03.791 --> 00:01:05.166
Dad.

8
00:01:05.250 --> 00:01:06.250
Dad.

9
00:01:56.375 --> 00:01:57.375
It's you.

10
00:02:00.666 --> 00:02:01.916
I'm Kolobe.

11
00:02:05.791 --> 00:02:07.125
Uncle!

12
00:02:51.208 --> 00:02:52.750
Zee. talk to me.

13
00:02:52.833 --> 00:02:54.083
<i>It was him.</i>

14
00:02:55.291 --> 00:02:57.416
- What are you talking about?
- <i>Uncle.</i>

15
00:02:58.125 --> 00:02:59.125
Uncle who?

16
00:02:59.208 --> 00:03:00.916
<i>Uncle. the caretaker.</i>

17
00:03:02.166 --> 00:03:03.500
Don and Grace's chemist.

18
00:03:03.583 --> 00:03:06.291
Don't lie. are you sure?

19
00:03:06.375 --> 00:03:09.666
I'm telling you.
As soon as I saw his face. I just froze.

20
00:03:11.708 --> 00:03:14.208
<i>Zinhle. can you get
another look just to be sure?</i>

21
00:03:15.083 --> 00:03:16.541
<i>Is he still there?</i>

22
00:03:19.833 --> 00:03:20.875
<i>I'll call you back.</i>

23
00:03:50.750 --> 00:03:52.291
I've been looking for you.

24
00:04:12.250 --> 00:04:13.250
I'm sorry.

25
00:05:53.375 --> 00:05:55.541
Have you seen the headline? Look.

26
00:06:00.375 --> 00:06:01.375
And Dad?

27
00:07:04.208 --> 00:07:05.208
You...

28
00:07:47.666 --> 00:07:50.000
Get the hell out of my house.

29
00:07:54.958 --> 00:07:56.000
Hey. girl!

30
00:08:18.458 --> 00:08:21.833
Where are you going? You also
running away from the drama in this house?

31
00:08:23.833 --> 00:08:24.875
With my friends.

32
00:08:26.458 --> 00:08:27.666
You and Linda...

33
00:08:36.041 --> 00:08:37.083
Do you love her?

34
00:08:38.791 --> 00:08:40.125
Very much.

35
00:08:48.583 --> 00:08:49.791
Who else could it be?

36
00:08:50.291 --> 00:08:52.750
She hates that Don chose Linda to be CEO...

37
00:09:02.291 --> 00:09:04.458
No. I don't care. You know. Don...

38
00:09:07.791 --> 00:09:10.500
- When I heard he's getting married again.
- Again?

39
00:09:17.291 --> 00:09:18.791
So you're really leaving?

40
00:09:22.416 --> 00:09:24.541
I don't think I'll be here
when you come back.

41
00:09:30.458 --> 00:09:32.000
I'll still see you around.

42
00:09:46.500 --> 00:09:49.333
We have to find out
what he does for Don and Grace.

43
00:09:49.416 --> 00:09:51.333
He introduced himself as Kolobe.

44
00:09:51.416 --> 00:09:54.000
I looked him up online
but couldn't find anything.

45
00:09:54.083 --> 00:09:56.875
You need his full name.

46
00:09:58.541 --> 00:09:59.666
Will you be okay?

47
00:10:01.791 --> 00:10:04.208
- I'll be fine.
- I know you really liked him.

48
00:10:04.791 --> 00:10:06.916
That's when I thought he was a good man.

49
00:10:09.083 --> 00:10:11.458
That's why you can't trust anyone.

50
00:10:12.958 --> 00:10:15.541
That's why you should stop
whatever you and Ndu are doing.

51
00:10:17.208 --> 00:10:20.000
I told you there's nothing going on.

52
00:10:22.208 --> 00:10:24.125
I'll let you know when I find his name.

53
00:10:24.208 --> 00:10:25.208
Bye.

54
00:10:48.583 --> 00:10:49.583
Tata.

55
00:10:53.583 --> 00:10:55.125
And get out of my house.

56
00:10:56.291 --> 00:10:57.333
Just like that?

57
00:11:02.958 --> 00:11:05.833
You can't make a decision like that
without talking to me first.

58
00:11:17.458 --> 00:11:21.375
My role in this company
has nothing to do with Thando and I.

59
00:11:22.750 --> 00:11:24.625
Grace did all of this. Dad.

60
00:11:36.916 --> 00:11:38.125
My...

61
00:11:38.208 --> 00:11:40.041
My relationship with Thando...

62
00:11:40.125 --> 00:11:42.208
- I tried...
- Thando is my wife!

63
00:12:26.875 --> 00:12:28.750
There's that big mouth again.

64
00:12:41.750 --> 00:12:43.125
You're better than this.

65
00:12:48.208 --> 00:12:51.291
You'll never get the kind of love
you need from Don.

66
00:12:51.375 --> 00:12:53.041
You'll have to imagine it.

67
00:12:59.916 --> 00:13:01.166
Thank you. Sisi.

68
00:15:08.875 --> 00:15:11.416
Angela's interviewing us tomorrow.

69
00:15:12.125 --> 00:15:14.708
It will help us present a united front.

70
00:15:28.208 --> 00:15:29.416
This thing with Linda...

71
00:15:42.625 --> 00:15:44.000
If I knew

72
00:15:44.916 --> 00:15:48.291
you and I would have
sorted it out quietly.

73
00:16:10.666 --> 00:16:11.833
Don't do this.

74
00:18:34.875 --> 00:18:35.875
Thank you.

75
00:19:01.041 --> 00:19:02.500
He's bald...

76
00:19:28.083 --> 00:19:30.750
Ndumiso. Your father wants to see you.

77
00:19:57.250 --> 00:19:58.416
Sit down.

78
00:21:43.125 --> 00:21:44.583
Mama. What's this about?

79
00:21:54.125 --> 00:21:55.166
What's up?

80
00:21:56.125 --> 00:21:57.166
What's going on?

81
00:22:02.416 --> 00:22:03.833
Between the two of you.

82
00:22:04.416 --> 00:22:06.416
Are you two in a serious relationship?

83
00:22:13.791 --> 00:22:16.083
I want you to do
the Durban shoot together.

84
00:22:18.333 --> 00:22:22.125
You've come out of your shell
since you started shooting with my son.

85
00:22:28.208 --> 00:22:29.750
But you do know that...

86
00:23:39.875 --> 00:23:40.958
Who am I?

87
00:23:41.666 --> 00:23:42.875
Thando. who am I?

88
00:23:48.500 --> 00:23:49.875
Who am I now?

89
00:23:52.750 --> 00:23:54.166
If I'm not a Bhengu?

90
00:25:24.375 --> 00:25:25.625
Please excuse us.

91
00:26:02.333 --> 00:26:03.500
Don't do that.

92
00:26:20.958 --> 00:26:23.833
I'm Calvin Madimetja Mamabolo.

93
00:26:23.916 --> 00:26:26.291
But you can call me Kolobe. Everyone does.

94
00:26:27.583 --> 00:26:28.708
Nice to meet you.

95
00:26:38.125 --> 00:26:40.375
Calvin Madimetja Mamabolo.

96
00:26:40.875 --> 00:26:43.708
Find out everything you can about him.

97
00:26:43.791 --> 00:26:45.625
We'll speak when I get back from Durban.

98
00:27:52.541 --> 00:27:54.958
What's up. my bro. are you good?

99
00:27:55.041 --> 00:27:57.625
I need a favor today.

100
00:27:58.125 --> 00:27:59.291
Are you free later?

101
00:28:01.625 --> 00:28:03.458
Don't worry. beers are on me.

102
00:28:04.291 --> 00:28:05.291
Cheers.

103
00:31:46.250 --> 00:31:47.250
Brother!

104
00:31:47.750 --> 00:31:49.083
- My brother.
- Hi.

105
00:31:49.166 --> 00:31:50.333
How are you?

106
00:31:50.416 --> 00:31:52.708
What do you use to shave? Huh?

107
00:31:53.291 --> 00:31:55.500
- A razor or shaving cream?
- Who are you?

108
00:31:56.000 --> 00:32:00.791
Look. I had a bad pie.
I need to use your toilet.

109
00:32:00.875 --> 00:32:03.208
- How is that my problem?
- Please help me.

110
00:32:03.291 --> 00:32:07.583
Please. he really needs to use the toilet.

111
00:32:08.708 --> 00:32:10.750
Please. my brother.

112
00:32:11.250 --> 00:32:12.916
Go that way...

113
00:32:13.000 --> 00:32:16.125
I won't find it. why don't
you just show me where it is.

114
00:32:16.208 --> 00:32:17.208
Let's go.

115
00:32:19.708 --> 00:32:20.833
My brother...

116
00:32:20.916 --> 00:32:23.250
- Are you okay?
- Thanks for helping me.

117
00:33:22.166 --> 00:33:23.291
Zinhle. look.

118
00:33:25.000 --> 00:33:26.375
We've got them.

119
00:33:27.791 --> 00:33:28.833
Look.

120
00:33:29.875 --> 00:33:30.916
Look.

121
00:33:32.916 --> 00:33:34.500
What are you doing?

122
00:33:34.583 --> 00:33:37.916
The cellphone signal in here is terrible.

123
00:33:39.166 --> 00:33:40.541
I wasn't doing anything.

124
00:33:40.625 --> 00:33:44.333
I was just struggling with the signal.
How do you get anything done around here?

125
00:34:17.916 --> 00:34:18.916
You came.

126
00:34:45.833 --> 00:34:46.833
Here you go.

127
00:34:53.416 --> 00:34:56.250
Have you met my family?
I'm always stressed.

128
00:35:01.916 --> 00:35:03.125
All of them.

129
00:35:06.750 --> 00:35:07.750
Tell me...

130
00:37:03.375 --> 00:37:04.541
What's wrong?

131
00:37:06.833 --> 00:37:08.000
I can't do this.

132
00:37:08.708 --> 00:37:11.833
- You can. You're the one who called me.
- It was a mistake.

133
00:37:12.750 --> 00:37:15.375
Grace. what do you get
for being faithful to a man...

134
00:37:16.458 --> 00:37:19.416
- Be careful of what you're saying.
- He doesn't want you.

135
00:37:23.666 --> 00:37:25.291
He doesn't respect you. Grace.

136
00:37:28.208 --> 00:37:30.541
Why are you wasting
your life with someone...

137
00:37:30.625 --> 00:37:33.791
Wait. Don't you dare lecture me.

138
00:37:36.166 --> 00:37:38.666
What have you been doing all this time?

139
00:37:40.833 --> 00:37:42.375
What kind of man does that?

140
00:37:42.458 --> 00:37:45.000
Then you spend years
serving Don like some garden boy?

141
00:37:45.083 --> 00:37:46.958
- Don't do that.
- Listen. Kolobe.

142
00:37:48.875 --> 00:37:50.541
I have money.

143
00:37:51.041 --> 00:37:53.208
I have children. I have everything.

144
00:37:56.291 --> 00:37:57.416
What about you?

145
00:37:57.500 --> 00:37:59.125
What do you have?

146
00:37:59.208 --> 00:38:00.708
- What do you have?
- Don't do this.

147
00:38:00.791 --> 00:38:02.125
You have nothing.

148
00:40:35.541 --> 00:40:36.666
I think you were right...

149
00:41:19.583 --> 00:41:20.583
<i>What about you?</i>

150
00:41:21.041 --> 00:41:22.291
<i>What do you have?</i>

151
00:41:22.791 --> 00:41:24.041
<i>What do you have?</i>

152
00:41:28.833 --> 00:41:30.000
<i>What do you have?</i>

153
00:42:53.041 --> 00:42:54.208
<i>Zinhle. look.</i>

154
00:42:59.458 --> 00:43:00.708
<i>We've got them.</i>

155
00:43:02.125 --> 00:43:03.166
<i>Look.</i>

156
00:43:04.125 --> 00:43:05.208
<i>Look.</i>

157
00:43:13.750 --> 00:43:14.875
- Bro.
- <i>Sure.</i>

158
00:43:16.041 --> 00:43:17.541
<i>Did you see the video?</i>

159
00:43:17.625 --> 00:43:20.791
- Yes. are you sure?
<i>- Yes. I'm sure.</i>

160
00:43:20.875 --> 00:43:27.333
<i>I broke into Kolobe's house
and heard him talk to Don about it.</i>

161
00:43:28.083 --> 00:43:32.666
<i>They're moving operations to China.
We need to make sure that we expose them.</i>

162
00:43:36.916 --> 00:43:39.041
Okay. I'll call you back.

163
00:44:26.958 --> 00:44:28.416
Zinhle. I'm falling for you.

164
00:44:30.916 --> 00:44:33.041
I've had my eyes on you...

165
00:44:46.750 --> 00:44:47.958
You must be joking...
